{{Top|leg}}
The '''logistics center''', also known as the '''logistics wing''', was the central facility from which the [[Republic Defense Procurement Office/Legends|Republic Defense Procurement office]] managed the distribution and transit of material and personnel in the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]].

The logistics center was largely manned by civilian personnel like [[Besany Wennen]] and [[Vinna Jiss]], assisted by [[Droid/Legends|droids]]. Only a few military troops were present, such as the injured [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone trooper]] [[Corr Skirata|CT-5108/8843]], known as "Corr", who was assigned there temporarily after losing his hands, as there was a shortage of sufficiently robust and sophisticated prosthetics, and he was unable to return immediately to front-line duties.

